{"tid":2464130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國以疫情為由煞停領養兒童計劃 美國400家庭無了期等候","createTime":"2021-03-27T08:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T09:35:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"797edadb8bb6edc940a76360c3a0148438c444b1","tid":2464130,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"一場武漢肺炎疫情，除了影響無數人的健康，各地的經濟活動之外，也影響到400個打算收養中國兒童的美國家庭。部分養父母指出，待收養的小孩有病，急需到美國治療，但現時只能無限期等待。<br />\n<br />\n韋爾奇（Welch）夫婦去年3月上旬已收拾好行李，預訂了酒店，準備出發到中國接家中第6個孩子，7歲的Penelope回家，但出發前夕收到通知，中國暫停計劃。行程原本押後數星期變成數月，至今已一年，仍然遙遙無期。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210327/D4JEMAGI5VB5HAWZPF43DBHEGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210327%2FD4JEMAGI5VB5HAWZPF43DBHEGM%2F&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr33lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=2bc33ee0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210327%2FD4JEMAGI5VB5HAWZPF43DBHEGM%2F&h=9c7e93f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210327/D4JEMAGI5VB5HAWZPF43DBHEGM/</a>"},{"pid":"2e9a3ff8a3f5c7bb7aa9de299d6c7b232ac4ea9b","tid":2464130,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010cb79b52d1d59b01de0c5d8464f81370039681","tid":2464130,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"咩世界？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3913aed978cd8a08b8bbfa9946d16c01fe7f03","tid":2464130,"uid":393145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"中國咁強大 <br />\n唔需要要水深火熱既美國人領養中國孩子啦<br />\n咩叫急需到美國治療?<br />\n中國火神山起咁撚快 又有歌聽<br />\n中國人權醫療教育